nodes.text: Liqueur was an alcoholic beverage. Types of liqueur included Cantonican cactus liqueur and Riosan liqueur. One night, when former Imperial loyalty officer Sinjir Rath Velus visited Pok's Place, a cantina on Akiva, he drunkenly addressed the bartender, a Mon Calamari named Pok, as "peddler of strange liqueurs". Drunk on mead and liqueur, he then proceeded to pick a fight with a group of Imperial soldiers.
